            Its history makes it abundantly clear that the CPC is capable of not only spearheading a great social revolution,
            </p>
            <p>
            也能够进行伟大的自我革命。<br/>
            but also imposing a great reform on itself.
            </p>
            <p>
            我们将继续清除一切侵蚀党的健康肌体的病毒，<br/>
