            深知和平的珍贵，发展的价值。<br/>
            These experiences have taught us that peace is precious and development must be valued.</p>
            <p>
            中国人民自信自尊，将坚定维护国家主权、安全、发展利益。<br/>
            With confidence and pride the Chinese people will be steadfast in upholding our country's sovereignty, security and development interests.</p>
            <p>
